quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  114,1,"Say, \"I seek refuge in the Lord of mankind"
  114,2,King of mankind
  114,3,One Whom mankind should worship
  114,4,"From the evil of the temptations, doubts and suggestions of the stealthy whisperer"
  114,5,— One who puts the evil things in minds of mankind —
  114,6,From among the jinn and mankind